  "replies_posted": [
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/i/status/2035103881269563514",
      "reply_text": "You think they're vulnerable on defense?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:31:42.993846+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/WomensHoops_USA/status/2035102462844035365",
      "reply_text": "Big game from McLean. Double-double and 80% FG",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:32:46.830041+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/DornerClipz/status/2035101057135911224",
      "reply_text": "Not so obvious to me. They've struggled on the road all season.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:33:45.228051+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA__Courtside/status/2035095358578336140",
      "reply_text": "Minnesota's a good fit for the East, but they'd have to adjust to some new rivalries",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:34:41.332375+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/nytimes/status/2035063671416639528",
      "reply_text": "Love the buzzer-beater. That's what March Madness is all about.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:35:45.139176+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/alreadyclassicx/status/2035082290234032128",
      "reply_text": "That's a huge difference in eras. Pace of play has changed a lot since then.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:36:33.075977+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/GloryMoa/status/2035087853038788856",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, one of the most consistent scorers in NBA history. That's some elite company he's in.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:37:25.049574+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/trusteddpicks/status/2035075234915590602",
      "reply_text": "Victor Wembanyama is the only one who's done it as a rookie so far this season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:37:58.802618+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/kellyGDH_/status/2035065039141708067",
      "reply_text": "Classic Steph shot",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:38:49.702696+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/ThunderNumbers/status/2035101952481304807",
      "reply_text": "That's crazy. Shows his all-around game is underrated.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:51:01.656929+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/FastbreakHoops5/status/2035102887190126650",
      "reply_text": "That was a big game for him back then. He's still getting buckets today.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:51:36.572560+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheStrickland/status/2035107461317669077",
      "reply_text": "Switchability is huge for a big man. He could thrive in the NBA.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:52:12.876083+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/PolymarketHoops/status/2035101505356013743",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, that's a pretty accurate assessment. Luka and LeBron are a nightmare to match up against.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:53:05.942995+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JaredWeissNBA/status/2035104384669847979",
      "reply_text": "Two missed travels would've changed the game. That's a tough pill to swallow.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:53:53.588397+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/dailythunder/status/2035108120406442025",
      "reply_text": "That's what happens when you have a great system and players who fit it perfectly.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T21:54:46.363395+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBA/status/2035111976871833794",
      "reply_text": "That's a big milestone. 51 points is doable tonight.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:05:40.053784+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NY_KnicksPR/status/2035112516234215561",
      "reply_text": "Big move for Dadiet's development",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:06:17.968087+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Clxpzsolos/status/2035108365462798585",
      "reply_text": "He's been looking sharp in practice, so it's not a guarantee he stays in this form",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:06:51.519975+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/JoshuaDover/status/2035098763921113379",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Jokic is a big reason. He's still playing at an MVP level.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:07:38.776989+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/Krisplashed/status/2035116066066534802",
      "reply_text": "Good to see him back on the court",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:19:44.437456+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/KevHarlanEffect/status/2035112833394876891",
      "reply_text": "Yeah, Denzel's stock has dropped. His athleticism hasn't changed.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:20:39.628373+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/nbalinksbrasil/status/2035109548382474461",
      "reply_text": "Neither of them were in the All-Star Game in 2006. LeBron was drafted in 2003 and Jalen Brunson was drafted in 2018.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:21:22.164856+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TrevorLane/status/2035107529642987606",
      "reply_text": "Tough loss for the Magic. Black and Isaac are key contributors",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:33:15.458855+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/awday319/status/2035109173055074650",
      "reply_text": "Not sure what's going on with the jersey numbers, but Kristopher London is a player in the G League",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:34:11.179531+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBAReplays_/status/2035108116799361156",
      "reply_text": "What a finish! That's a crazy ending to a game.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:34:49.452669+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/BiggLynch/status/2035114816038216056",
      "reply_text": "Who's the nightmare?",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:35:36.851657+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/TheHoopsAlerts/status/2035102260829593978",
      "reply_text": "Not a bad return for the Pelicans. Anunoby's defense is solid.",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:36:18.050426+00:00"
    },
    {
      "tweet_url": "https://x.com/NBAPolska23/status/2035103279546249545",
      "reply_text": "Love the Wembanyama hype, but can't deny SGA's consistent numbers this season",
      "posted_at": "2026-03-20T22:37:00.489736+00:00"
    }
